  <li id="comment-5617" class="comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1">
    <header class="comment--meta">
      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn"><a href="http://smittenkitchen.com" class="url" rel="ugc external nofollow">deb</a></cite></div>
      <a href="https://orangette.net/2006/10/big-bad-banana/#comment-5617"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2006-10-10T16:41:00-04:00">Tuesday, October 10, 2006 at 4:41 pm</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>If it makes you feel any better, my banana confession is even more self-indicting. You see, I love the brown, spotty overripe banana and it horrifies everyone around me, so I eat them privately. Quietly. Only the lady at the bodega where I get my morning yogurt knows I bypass all the bright yellow healthy ones for the unlovable, about-to-be tossed one in the corner. And my husband, who would much rather me bake them into this cake. Understandably, too &#8211; it looks lovely!</p>
    </div>

