      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn"><a href="https://www.blogger.com/profile/01493708300940204826" class="url" rel="ugc external nofollow">Molly</a></cite></div>
      <a href="https://orangette.net/2006/10/big-bad-banana/#comment-5659"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2009-01-19T01:12:00-05:00">Monday, January 19, 2009 at 1:12 am</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Sorry for the confusion, Lin, but the recipe here is correct. 1 stick of butter is indeed 4 ounces, and 4 ounces equals 1/2 cup.  I get confused about all that sometimes too, but it&#8217;s correct&#8230;</p>
    </div>

      </li><!-- #comment-## -->
  <li id="comment-5660" class="comment even thread-even depth-1">
    <header class="comment--meta">
      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn"><a href="http://expiring.blogspot.com" class="url" rel="ugc external nofollow">selena</a></cite></div>
